data.description: Located in the sloping foothills of East Alamogordo in a Planned Unit Development. Don't miss viewing this Territorial style townhome.  All the amenities you're looking for and expect in a newer home.  How about Tile Flooring..Large open living room.. Fireplace.. View of the mountains framed in the picture window.. Formal dining area.. Large galley kitchen with pantry and Granite counter tops..Built-in desk.. Great Main suite with lots of storage and closets..Tile showers.. and an extra room for guests.  AND a 2 car garage. " Be home for the Holidays"
